TextEng: What would you give me to spare your life?
I've made a decision. It's time to die.
I have no interest in this anymore. I'm leaving.
What you give me if me let you live?
No thanks. Me here to kill you.
Uh, me go now.
That sounds like a deal.
Yuh, okay. Fair deal, then.
Who are you?
Me not know who you is.
No deals. I'm here for your death.
Me not here for talk, but for death. Your death!
Text: 나 얘기하러 온 거 아니야. 죽이러 온 거야. 네 죽음!

TextEng: What's this about bounty hunters?
Delilah! You criminal. Me hear about you.
Text: 딜라일라! 넌 범죄자야. 나 너 얘기 들었어.

TextEng: Delilah! You're one of the escaped convicts I've been told about.
Text: 딜라일라! 네가 소문으로 듣던 탈옥 죄수 중 하나구나.

TextEng: Me not knows what means by bounty hunter.
Fine. Tell me of your efforts.
Okay. Me listens. You talk.
I'll let you go if you make it worthwhile to me.
Me could let you go if me gets something.
Sounds like you understand. Now, let's fight.
Me thinks you got it. We fight now?
No. I want the truth, or I kill you.
Text: 안 돼. 진실을 말해. 안 그럼 죽여.

TextEng: Me hears full story, or me kills you.
Uh, yeah... okay. I'll leave you alone.
Me not care. Me leave. You stay living.
I cannot let you leave until I know the full story.
Text: 전부 듣기 전엔 보내줄 수 없어.

TextEng: Me wants hearing full story!
Your past? Freedom? What do you mean?
You're free now. How did you manage to escape?
You free now. How you escape?
I think I've heard enough, convict. Time to die.
Me hears enough, criminals. You die now.
Who were the other inmates?
Go on.
Me want to hear more.
You're nothing but a common criminal. Time for you to die.
Text: 넌 그냥 평범한 범죄자야. 죽을 시간이야.

TextEng: You criminal. You die now.
Who were other inmates? Please tell me.
I've heard enough of this. Time to die.
Hmm... me hears enough. Time to die.
What you means of past and freedom?
I'm not here to talk. It's time for you to die.
Text: 얘기하러 온 게 아니야. 죽을 시간이야.

TextEng: Me not want talking. You die now.
I'm done talking. It's time for you to die.
Me done talking. You die now!
What are you getting at?
What you mean?
Well it has been a long time, and you're definitely not sore on the eyes.
Text: 그래 오래됐지, 그리고 넌 확실히 볼만하네.

TextEng: It has been long time. You are pretty girl.
What do you want me to do?
What you want me do?
Okay.
